<br>
The leader and cleric were in the same guild.  I gave the cleric 5 peri's to cover my symbols.  The leader then stated that all sellables go to the cleric period.  <br>
<br>
Well this just pissed me off.  I paid for my symbols, personally. I am not here to subsidize every lamer that is too greedy/lazy to make sure the cleric gets compensated.  I do that for myself and possibly any friends that need it, but hell no, just because that cleric can't make money in other pickup groups doesn't mean they need to take my share of the loot now.  <br>
<br>
That method is way too communist for me and what ends up happening is the SAME people who have never bought a peridot but demand symbol, the SAME people who never have food and tell the group, &quot;anyone got some spare food?&quot; are the ones that constantly leech off the responsible people.<br>
<br>
If I supply reagents, then I want my percentage of the loot.  There is nothing wrong with that.<br>
