Honestly, I'll take HS over Seb any day of the week.  Velks is a bit of a stretch I admit (I go there a lot, I know it's out of the way though), and The Hole, well I follow Brell so I don't hunt their either.  But, combine all those with KC and all the other places that higher level clerics can go, and mature the server a bit, and it balences out.  There's no way you can tell me at any given moment most of the pickup clerics are in Seb - it just doesn't support that many people, although yeah, clerics are certianly incentivized to go.<br>
